gai Desam]]'' (2002)\n|-\n| ''[[Vinaya Vidheya Rama]]'' (2019)\n|-\n| [[Radha (actress)|Radha]] || ''[[Enga Chinna Raasa]]'' (1987)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Meenakshi Sheshadri]] || ''[[Duet (1994 film)|Duet]]'' (1994)\n|-\n|''[[Aapadbandhavudu]]'' (1992)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Aamani]] || ''[[Subha Lagnam]]'' (1994)\n|-\n| ''[[Maavichiguru]]'' (1996)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[Vijayashanti]] || \n''[[Mondi Mogudu Penki Pellam]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''[[Police Lockup]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''[[Mannan (film)|Mannan]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''[[Karthavyam (1990 film)|Kartavyam]]'' (1990)\n|-\n| ''[[Kondaveeti Donga]]'' (1990)\n|-\n| ''[[Padamati Sandhya Ragam]]'' (1987)\n|-\n| ''[[Pratighatana]]'' (1985)\n|-\n| Aparna || ''[[Sundarakanda (1992 film)|Sundarakanda]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| [[Sudha Chandran]] || ''[[Mayuri (film)|Mayuri]]'' (1985)\n|-\n| [[Sushmita Sen]] || ''[[Ratchagan]]'' (1997)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Tabu (actress)|Tabu]] || ''[[Snehithiye]]'' (2000)\n|-\n| ''[[Kadhal Desam]]'' (1996)\n|-\n| [[Jayabharathi]] || ''[[Varusham Padhinaaru]]'' (1989)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Kushboo]] || ''[[Stalin (2006 film)|Stalin]]'' (2006)\n|-\n|''[[Agnyaathavaasi]]'' (2018)\n|-\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:50px;\"| Year\n! style=\"width:300px;\"| Title\n! style=\"width:150px;\"| Role\n! style=\"width:150px;\"| Language\n|-\n| 2005-2007\n| ''Selvi''\n| Thamarai\n|Tamil\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|id=0765248|name=Saritha}}\n\n{{FilmfareTamilBestActress}}\n{{TamilNaduStateAwardForBestActress}}\n{{Karnataka State Award for Best Actress}}\n{{FilmfareKannadaBestActress}}\n{{NandiSpecialJuryAward}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Indian film actresses]]\n[[Category:Indian voice actresses]]\n[[Category:Indian television actresses]]\n[[Category:Tamil Nadu State Film Awards winners]]\n[[Category:Filmfare Awards South winners]]\n[[Category:Actresses i